10 roundtrips earn you a
free roundtrip and more.
Southwest Airlines has created a
frequent flyer program that doesn't short-
change people who take short flights:
The Company Club.
To join, take 10 roundtrips (or 20 one-
way trips) on the The Company Plane*
and you'll receive your membership card
and a free roundtrip to any of the exciting
cities we serve in the continental U.S.
